Ashley Naylor (born 23 August 1960) is a former English professional squash player.
Naylor was born on 23 August 1960 and lived in Batley, Yorkshire. He first took up squash in 1973 and became Yorkshire champion in 1983 and 1984. He became a full English international in 1980.
